column5: The board will be down for a tuneup. The scheduled downtime is tonight at 23:00 and maybe again at 03:00. Total downtime will be 1 to 2 hours. This is just a heads up to let you know that we're not asleep at the switch even though at times, we may appear to be. Sorry for the inconvenience and thank you for understanding.
Maybe I'll actually have to turn on the TV
